***VOTING ELIGIBILITY***
     We should receive 3 inputs from the user
     1st input: name of the person
     2nd input: gender of the person
     3rd input: age of the person
     . criteria1: less than 18 yrs [irrespective of gender]
     . criteria2: if some one more that 60 yrs [irrespective of gender]
     . criteria3: if gender is male they have rights to vote only if they are above 30 yrs

-> Program:
name = str(input("Enter name: "))
gender = str(input("Enter gender: "))
age = int(input("Enter age: "))
if age < 18:
    print("Not eligible")

elif age > 60:
    print("Eligible")

else:
    if gender == "M" and age > 30:
      print("Eligible")
    else:
      print("Not Eligible")




